INSERT INTO
			Jumpstats (
				type,
				mode_id,
				style_id,
				strafes,
				distance,
				sync,
				pre,
				max,
				overlap,
				bad_air,
				dead_air,
				height,
				airpath,
				deviation,
				average_width,
				airtime,
				player_id,
				server_id,
				plugin_version_id
			)
		VALUES
			(?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
